  <title>Save PO file</title>

  <p>Each time you edit the PO file (by changing the translated string or the information in a header), an asterisk “*” sign appears before its name in the window title. This indicates that there are changes in the file. You can save your changes by pressing the  <gui style="button">Save</gui> in the header bar or using the <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>S</key></keyseq> keyboard shortcut.</p>

 <p>To save the PO file with a different name, press the button next to <gui style="button">Save</gui> in the header bar or the <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Shift</key><key>S</key></keyseq> keyboard shortcut.
</p>

